<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>jǐn guǎn tā 迦南290</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 jǐn guǎn tā yī hǎo duō rén de bìng, jǐn guǎn tā kāi xiā zi de yǎn jīng,
 jǐn guǎn tā wèi quán rén lèi shě mìng hái yǒu rén hèn è tā duì tā de ài bù dǒng.
 tiān qǐ liáng fēng, shù yè diāo líng, rén shì jiān méi yǒu yī diǎn zhēn qíng.
 rì yǐng fēi qù, hēi yè lái dào, wéi yǒu yǐ sè liè jiā liàng zhe dēng.
 zǒu ba tóng gōng zài hēi yè lǐ bǎ rén huàn xǐng, wǒ men yī tóng jǐng xǐng dào tiān míng.
 zǒu ba tóng gōng zài hēi yè lǐ bǎ rén huàn xǐng, wǒ men yī tóng jǐng xǐng dào tiān míng.</lyrics>
